Ishyirahamwe ryo kubungabunga inyamaswa zo mu Rwanda (mu [[Icyongereza|cyongereza]]: Rwanda Wildlife Conservation Association [RWCA]) yashinzwe na Dr. Olivier NSENGIMANA mu 2015 kugira ngo ikureho ubucuruzi butemewe bw’inyamaswa nk'imisambi ([[:en:Grey_crowned_crane|Gray Crowned Crane]]) mu [[Rwanda]] no kwagura ibikorwa by'ubushakashatsi no kubungabunga andi moko yangiritse kandi abangamiwe mu Rwanda no mu karere ka Afurika y’iburasirazuba.<ref name=":0">https://futurefornature.org/an-extraordinary-year-for-rwanda-wildlife-conservation-association/?gclid=Cj0KCQjwjN-SBhCkARIsACsrBz68JeMSc47FM60mqs3dbll5GOjfC5YVnNcVMswMq1WRwxyEsnC_H-IaAk4nEALw_wcB</ref><ref>https://www.bornfree.org.uk/rwca</ref>

== Ubutumwa ==
[[Dosiye:Grey_Crowned_Crane_(Balearica_regulorum)_(8290734959).jpg|thumb|Grey Crowned Crane (Balearica regulorum)]]
Inshingano z'umuryango wacu ni ugutanga ibisubizo birambye kubibazo bikomeye byo kubungabunga inyamaswa mu Rwanda no mukarere ka Afrika yuburasirazuba dukoresheje uburyo bwose bushoboka na disipulini nyinshi nk'inzira imwe yadufasha kugera k'ubuzima bw'imyamaswa neza<ref>https://www.tusk.org/projects/rwanda-wildlife-conservation-association/</ref><ref>https://futurefornature.org/an-extraordinary-year-for-rwanda-wildlife-conservation-association/</ref>.

== Ubushakashatsi ==
[[Dosiye:Grey_Crowned_Crane_Balearica_regulorum_Tanzania_4328_Nevit.jpg|thumb|Grey Crowned Crane Balearica regulorum Tanzania]]
Mu ibarura ryabo ryambere ryigihugu rya Gray Crowned Crane muri 2017, babonye crane 487. Muri 2019 umubare wa crane wabonetse wageze kuri 748! RWCA ikora ibarura ikoresheje ubushakashatsi mu kirere no ku butaka. RWCA yashyizeho itsinda ry'abantu 30 bashinzwe kubungabunga ibidukikije bakorera mu bice by'igihugu kandi bahora babika amashusho ya Gray Crowned Cranes bakoresheje porogaramu yihariye. Muri 2019 hakozwe inyandiko 1045 zo kureba hamwe namakuru ajyanye nimyororokere yizi nyamaswa naho zikunda gutura.<ref name=":0" />

== Amateka ya Grey crowned crane ==
[[Dosiye:Grey_crowned_crane_(Balearica_regulorum).jpg|thumb|Grey crowned crane (Balearica regulorum)]]
The Grey crowned Crane, ifitanye isano rya hafi na black crowned crane<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Black_crowned_crane</ref>, kandi ubwo bwoko bwombi bwagiye bufatwa nkubwoko bumwe. Bwombi buratandukanye hashingiwe ku bimenyetso bya genetike, guhamagarwa, plumage n'ibice byambaye ubusa nka maguru, kandi abategetsi bose babifata nk'ubwoko butandukanye muri iki gihe<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grey_crowned_crane#cite_note-hbw-3</ref>. Hariho ubwoko bubiri, muri afurika y'iburasirazuba B.r. gibbericeps (crested crane) buherereye m'uburasirazuba bwa repubulika iharanira demokarasi ya [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo|Kongo]] no muri [[Ubugande|Uganda]], iyo nyoni ihagarariwe mu ibendera ry'igihugu<ref>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flag_of_Uganda</ref><ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20170528162336/http://gov.ug/about-uganda/sector/national-symbols</ref>, na [[Kenya]] muburasirazuba bwa Afrika yepfo. Ifite ahantu hanini h'uruhu rutukura rwambaye ubusa hejuru yuruhu rwera kuruta ubwoko buto butoranijwe, B. r. regulorum (outh African crowned crane), yororoka kuva Angola yepfo kugera muri Afrika yepfo.

